headline: Lowe's CEO: How to get ahead without an 'impressive pedigree' or standout resume—you'll ‘get people to notice you'
summary: If you don't have a flashy resume or an impressive professional background, the best way to get noticed is to vie for an undesirable job, says Lowe's CEO.

headline: Wall Street sinks as Trump threatens 8 European countries with tariffs over Greenland
summary: Stocks slumped on Wall Street Tuesday after President Donald Trump threatened to hit eight European countries with new tariffs as tensions escalate over his attempts to assert American control over Greenland.  Technology stocks were the heaviest weights on the market.  Nvidia, one of the most valuable companies in the world, plunged 4.4%.
